  <recitals>
    <recital>
      <conjunction>WHEREAS,</conjunction>
      <text>The Stockbridge-Munsee Community, Band of Mohican Indians, is a federally recognized Indian tribe governed by the Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council pursuant to authority vested in the Council by a Constitution approved in November 1937; and</text>
    </recital>
    <recital>
      <conjunction>WHEREAS,</conjunction>
      <text>The Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council has the authority under its Constitution and its inherent rights as a sovereign nation to act on behalf of the Community in area of economic affairs and other issues of self-governance; and</text>
    </recital>
    <recital>
      <conjunction>WHEREAS,</conjunction>
      <text>The Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council is the final forum for determinations of tribal membership; and</text>
    </recital>
    <recital>
      <conjunction>WHEREAS,</conjunction>
      <text>The Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council desires to clarify the manner in which tribal membership appeals will be processed in the final forum;</text>
    </recital>
    <recital>
      <conjunction>NOW THEREFORE BE IT RESOLVED,</conjunction>
      <text>the Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council hereby adopts the amendments to Chapter 44, which include the following changes:</text>
      <text>
        <ul proof="needed">
          <li>Deleting <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.6" proof="needed">Section 44.6</cite>; and</li>
          <li>Renumbering <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.7" proof="needed">44.7</cite>; <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.8" proof="needed">44.8</cite>; <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.9" proof="needed">44.9</cite>; <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.10" proof="needed">44.10</cite>; and</li>
          <li>Creating new Sections <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.6|(C)" proof="needed">44.6 (C)</cite> (5) (a) and (b); and</li>
          <li>Renumbering <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.6|(C)" proof="needed">Section 44.6 (C)</cite> (5) (c);and</li>
          <li>Creating new <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.6|(D)" proof="needed">Section 44.6 (D)</cite>; and</li>
          <li>Renumbering Sections <cite doc="Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code" path="44.6|(E)" proof="needed">44.6 (E)</cite>.</li>
        </ul>
      </text>
